      <div class="sz-why-card sz-why-card--good">
        <div class="sz-why-icon">✓</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="sz-why-card-title">Smooth, Permanent Finish</h3>
          <p class="sz-why-card-text">The ink becomes part of the bottle itself. No raised edges, no texture change—just a seamless, professional look.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="sz-why-card sz-why-card--good">
        <div class="sz-why-icon">✓</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="sz-why-card-title">Dishwasher Friendly</h3>
          <p class="sz-why-card-text">Sublimation won't peel or crack from washing. We recommend hand wash for longevity, but it can handle the dishwasher.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="sz-why-card sz-why-card--good">
        <div class="sz-why-icon">✓</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="sz-why-card-title">Vibrant, Fade-Resistant</h3>
          <p class="sz-why-card-text">Colors stay bright and true even after months of daily use. Your bottle looks as good as day one.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="sz-why-card sz-why-card--bad">
        <div class="sz-why-icon">✗</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="sz-why-card-title">Not Like Vinyl Stickers</h3>
          <p class="sz-why-card-text">Vinyl decals sit on top of the surface, eventually peeling at the edges, cracking, and looking worn out.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="sz-why-comparison">
      <div class="sz-why-compare-col sz-why-compare-col--us">
        <p class="sz-why-compare-label">Shelzy's Sublimation</p>
        <ul class="sz-why-compare-list">
